ingredient: 1 15 oz. can fire roasted diced tomatoes
1/4 cup heavy cream, plus more for brushing crust edges
2 Tbsp chopped fresh Italian parsley for garnish (optional)
12 oz. frozen vegetables (corn, carrots, green beans)
1 tsp active dry or instant yeast
1.5 cups all-purpose flour (plus some for dusting)
2 cups cooked chicken, shredded or chopped**
